quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,41,"Koo shololangakhwo mbu bitsoominjia Nyasaye ebili mwikulu nende khushialo nende amayoni olwakafimbulanga tsimbaya tsiako buli bioosi biamanya isaala yiyie, nende injila yokhumwitsoomeliamwo. Ne Nyasaye ni Omumanyi muno khukabakholanga"
  24,42,Ne ni obwa Nyasaye obwami bwomwikulu nende khushialo ne ewa Nyasaye ni amakalushilo kaboosi
  24,43,"Koo! Shololangakhwo mbu Nyasaye ayilaanga amaleesi mana akaretsanga halala, mana akakhole libunjikho? Mana olalola ifula nirula hakari wako , naye yeshinjia okhurula hekulu khutsingulu etsia maleesi ifula yamachina mana atililakho owayenya ne eyile ehale khu owayenya okhumiesukha khwelikulu khukhaaba okhuwofusia tsimoni"
  24,44,Nyasaye akalukhaninjia eshilo nende eshitere toto mu ako khulimwo nende eshimanyisio khubandu abamachesi
  24,45,"Ne Nyasaye yaloonga buli isolo okhurulana nende amatsi, etsindi tsiatsio tsichendelanga inda yatsio, ne etsindi tsichendelanga amakulu kabili, ne etsindi natsio tsichendelanga amakulu kane, Nyasaye aloonganga shiayenya toto Nyasaye ni Omunyali wabuli eshindu"
  24,46,Toto khweshia tsinyaali etsinoosinjia ne Nyasaye alunjisinjia owayenya khunjila ingololofu
  24,47,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “ khusuubile Nyasaye nende Omurumwa, ne khuwulile” 24. mana abandi mubo imbeli wakano bakakhayanga, ne abo shibali basuubila tawe"
  24,48,"Ne nibalangwa khu Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe kho ababusilie hakari wabu, abandi mubo bakhayanga ako"
  24,49,"Ne nibali mbu nibo bali khubwatoto , bamwitsilanga lwangu nibehotselesiye"
  24,50,"Koo bali nende obulwale mumioyo chiabu , nohomba bali nende tsinganakani nohomba baritsanga mbu Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe balabakholela obubii! Halali abo nibo Ababii"